    "high_score_system": "Yes, a local high score system will track the top 5 scores, saved using localStorage. Scores are accumulated across levels.",
    "score_display": "The current score will be displayed prominently in the top-right corner of the screen as 'Score: [###]'. Below it, 'Level: [X]' and 'Time: [MM:SS]' (top-left) and 'Dissatisfied: [X]/[Y]' (bottom-right).",
